{"data":[{"name":"99:1","price":"ഭൂമി പ്രകമ്പനം കൊള്ളിക്കപ്പെട്ടാല്‍ - അതിന്‍റെ ഭയങ്കരമായ ആ പ്രകമ്പനം.","arabic":"إِذَا زُلۡزِلَتِ ٱلۡأَرۡضُ زِلۡزَالَهَا","category":["99 (Az-Zalzalah)","Az-Zalzalah","Surah Az-Zalzalah"],"ayahNumber":6139,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ml","meta":{"transliteration":"idhā zul'zilati al-arḍu zil'zālahā ","translations":["When","is shaken","the earth","(with) its earthquake","(1)"],"transliterationArr":["idhā","zul'zilati","al-arḍu","zil'zālahā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,690],[2,690,1730],[3,1730,2580],[4,2580,4295]]}},{"name":"99:2","price":"ഭൂമി അതിന്‍റെ ഭാരങ്ങള്‍ പുറം തള്ളിയാൽ,","arabic":"وَأَخۡرَجَتِ ٱلۡأَرۡضُ أَثۡقَالَهَا","category":["99 (Az-Zalzalah)","Az-Zalzalah","Surah Az-Zalzalah"],"ayahNumber":6140,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ml","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-akhrajati al-arḍu athqālahā ","translations":["And brings forth","the earth","its burdens","(2)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-akhrajati","al-arḍu","athqālahā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1380],[2,1380,2170],[3,2170,3865]]}},{"name":"99:3","price":"അതിന് എന്തുപറ്റി എന്ന് മനുഷ്യന്‍ പറയുകയും ചെയ്താല്‍.(1)","arabic":"وَقَالَ ٱلۡإِنسَٰنُ مَا لَهَا","category":["99 (Az-Zalzalah)","Az-Zalzalah","Surah Az-Zalzalah"],"ayahNumber":6141,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"1) അന്ത്യദിനത്തിലുണ്ടാകുന്ന സംഭവങ്ങളത്രെ ഇവിടെ പ്രതിപാദിക്കപ്പെടുന്നത്.","lang":"ml","meta":{"transliteration":"waqāla al-insānu mā lahā ","translations":["And says","man","What","(is) with it","(3)"],"transliterationArr":["waqāla","al-insānu","mā","lahā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,930],[2,930,3310],[3,3310,3790],[4,3790,4495]]}},{"name":"99:4","price":"അന്നേ ദിവസം അത് (ഭൂമി) അതിന്‍റെ വര്‍ത്തമാനങ്ങള്‍ പറഞ്ഞറിയിക്കുന്നതാണ്‌.","arabic":"يَوۡمَئِذٖ تُحَدِّثُ أَخۡبَارَهَا","category":["99 (Az-Zalzalah)","Az-Zalzalah","Surah Az-Zalzalah"],"ayahNumber":6142,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ml","meta":{"transliteration":"yawma-idhin tuḥaddithu akhbārahā ","translations":["That Day","it will report","its news","(4)"],"transliterationArr":["yawma-idhin","tuḥaddithu","akhbārahā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2180],[2,2180,3220],[3,3220,4875]]}},{"name":"99:5","price":"നിന്‍റെ രക്ഷിതാവ് അതിന് ബോധനം നല്‍കിയത് നിമിത്തം.","arabic":"بِأَنَّ رَبَّكَ أَوۡحَىٰ لَهَا","category":["99 (Az-Zalzalah)","Az-Zalzalah","Surah Az-Zalzalah"],"ayahNumber":6143,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ml","meta":{"transliteration":"bi-anna rabbaka awḥā lahā ","translations":["Because","your Lord","inspired","[to] it","(5)"],"transliterationArr":["bi-anna","rabbaka","awḥā","lahā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1750],[2,1750,2690],[3,2690,3560],[4,3560,4215]]}},{"name":"99:6","price":"അന്നേ ദിവസം മനുഷ്യര്‍ പല സംഘങ്ങളായി പുറപ്പെടുന്നതാണ്‌. അവര്‍ക്ക് അവരുടെ കര്‍മ്മങ്ങള്‍ കാണിക്കപ്പെടേണ്ടതിനായിട്ട്‌.","arabic":"يَوۡمَئِذٖ يَصۡدُرُ ٱلنَّاسُ أَشۡتَاتٗا لِّيُرَوۡاْ أَعۡمَٰلَهُمۡ","category":["99 (Az-Zalzalah)","Az-Zalzalah","Surah Az-Zalzalah"],"ayahNumber":6144,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ml","meta":{"transliteration":"yawma-idhin yaṣduru al-nāsu ashtātan liyuraw aʿmālahum ","translations":["That Day","will proceed","the mankind","(in) scattered groups","to be shown","their deeds","(6)"],"transliterationArr":["yawma-idhin","yaṣduru","al-nāsu","ashtātan","liyuraw","aʿmālahum",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2010],[2,2010,2830],[3,2830,4460],[4,4460,5540],[5,5540,6560],[6,6560,8515]]}},{"name":"99:7","price":"അപ്പോള്‍ ആര്‍ ഒരു അണുവിന്‍റെ തൂക്കം നന്മ ചെയ്തിരുന്നുവോ അവനത് കാണും.","arabic":"فَمَن يَعۡمَلۡ مِثۡقَالَ ذَرَّةٍ خَيۡرٗا يَرَهُۥ","category":["99 (Az-Zalzalah)","Az-Zalzalah","Surah Az-Zalzalah"],"ayahNumber":6145,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ml","meta":{"transliteration":"faman yaʿmal mith'qāla dharratin khayran yarahu ","translations":["So whoever","does","(equal to the) weight","(of) an atom","good","will see it","(7)"],"transliterationArr":["faman","yaʿmal","mith'qāla","dharratin","khayran","yarahu",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,580],[2,580,2140],[3,2140,3250],[4,3250,4250],[5,4250,5050],[6,5050,7025]]}},{"name":"99:8","price":"ആര്‍ ഒരു അണുവിന്‍റെ തൂക്കം തിന്മ ചെയ്തിരുന്നുവോ അവന്‍ അതും കാണും.(2)","arabic":"وَمَن يَعۡمَلۡ مِثۡقَالَ ذَرَّةٖ شَرّٗا يَرَهُۥ","category":["99 (Az-Zalzalah)","Az-Zalzalah","Surah Az-Zalzalah"],"ayahNumber":6146,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"2) ഇഹലോകത്ത് മനുഷ്യന്‍ ചെയ്ത ഏത് നിസ്സാരമായ പ്രവൃത്തിക്കും കണിശമായ പ്രതിഫലം പരലോകത്ത് അല്ലാഹു നല്കുന്നതാണ് എന്നര്‍ത്ഥം.","lang":"ml","meta":{"transliteration":"waman yaʿmal mith'qāla dharratin sharran yarahu ","translations":["And whoever","does","(equal to the) weight","(of) an atom","evil","will see it","(8)"],"transliterationArr":["waman","yaʿmal","mith'qāla","dharratin","sharran","yarahu",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,550],[2,550,2460],[3,2460,3640],[4,3640,4820],[5,4820,6790],[6,6790,9315]]}}],"chapter":["99 (Az-Zalzalah)","Az-Zalzalah","Surah Az-Zalzalah","Chapter Az-Zalzalah","Zalzalah","Surah Zalzalah","Chapter Zalzalah","Az Zalzalah","Surah Az Zalzalah","Chapter Az Zalzalah","Surah 99","Chapter 99","The Earthquake","الزلزلة"],"version":{"key":"malayalam_kunhi","direction":"ltr","language_iso_code":"ml","version":"1.0.3","last_update":1622322000,"title":"Malayalam translation - Abdul-Hamid Haidar Al-Madany and Kanhi Muhammad","description":"Translation of the Quran meanings into Malayalam by Abdul-Hamid Haidar Al-Madany and Kanhi Muhammad."}}